  "difficultyLevel": 5,
  "lyrics": "Oh yeah, I can't breathe, can't breathe, I can't breathe When I exhale, I touch my pain with my wishes and I wish them well I can't breathe, I'm waiting for the exhale Touch my pain with my wishes and I wish them well Still no life, but oh well I still try even though I know I'm gon' fail Stress on my shoulder like an anvil Work it got me itching like I need help Throat's killing me, I'm bleeding on help Sometimes I just don't know how to fail Phone call from depression Use my past and my memories as a weapon On the other line, talk talk to addiction Speaking of the drugs, I miss them This can't be real, is it fiction? Something is broken again I cry out for help, do they listen? I'ma be alone until the finish This is the part where I tell you I'm fine but I'm lying I just don't want you to worry This is the part where I take all my feelings and hide them Cause I don't want nobody to hurt me, can't breathe I'm waiting for the exhale Touch my pain with my wishes and I wish them well Still no life, but oh well I still try even though I know I'm gon' fail Stress on my shoulder like an anvil Work it got me itching like I need help Drugs are killing me, I'm bleeding on help Sometimes I just don't know how to fail Hell, but let's keep it real If it wasn't for these pills, I wouldn't be here What if I keep taking these pills, I wouldn't be here Yeah, must have told you all my secrets Yeah, they're killing me to pieces I really think I need them I stopped taking the drugs and then the drugs take me This is the part where I tell you I'm fine but I'm lying Cause I just don't want you to worry This is the part where I take all my feelings and hide them Cause I don't want nobody to hurt me, can't breathe I'm waiting for the exhale Touch my pain with my wishes and I wish them well Still no life, but oh well Still try even though I know I'm gon' fail Stress on my shoulder like an anvil Work it got me itching like I need help Drugs are killing me, I'm bleeding on help Sometimes I just don't know how to fail Sometimes I just don't know how to feel This is the part where I tell you I'm fine This is the part where I take all my feelings and hide them Cause I don't want nobody to hurt me, can't breathe  Touch my pain with my wishes and I wish them well  Stress on my shoulder like an anvil   Sometimes I just don't know how to feel This is the part where I tell you I'm fine",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 12.800000190734863,
      "text": "Oh yeah, I can't breathe, can't breathe, I can't breathe",
      "start": 3.5199999809265137
    },
    {
      "end": 22.739999771118164,
      "text": "When I exhale, I touch my pain with my wishes and I wish them well",
      "start": 13.420000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 27.739999771118164,
      "text": "I can't breathe, I'm waiting for the exhale",
      "start": 25
    },
    {
      "end": 31.399999618530273,
      "text": "Touch my pain with my wishes and I wish them well",
      "start": 28.299999237060547
    },
    {
      "end": 34.68000030517578,
      "text": "Still no life, but oh well",
      "start": 31.399999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 37.900001525878906,
      "text": "I still try even though I know I'm gon' fail",
      "start": 34.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 40.7400016784668,
      "text": "Stress on my shoulder like an anvil",
      "start": 38.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 44.380001068115234,
      "text": "Work it got me itching like I need help",
      "start": 41.5
    },
    {
      "end": 47.599998474121094,
      "text": "Throat's killing me, I'm bleeding on help",
      "start": 44.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 51.619998931884766,
      "text": "Sometimes I just don't know how to fail",
      "start": 48.060001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 53.880001068115234,
      "text": "Phone call from depression",
      "start": 51.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 57,
      "text": "Use my past and my memories as a weapon",
      "start": 53.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 60.2400016784668,
      "text": "On the other line, talk talk to addiction",
      "start": 57.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 64.19999694824219,
      "text": "Speaking of the drugs, I miss them",
      "start": 60.779998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 66.68000030517578,
      "text": "This can't be real, is it fiction?",
      "start": 64.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 69.45999908447266,
      "text": "Something is broken again",
      "start": 67.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 73.45999908447266,
      "text": "I cry out for help, do they listen?",
      "start": 70.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 76.33999633789062,
      "text": "I'ma be alone until the finish",
      "start": 73.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 80.5999984741211,
      "text": "This is the part where I tell you I'm fine but I'm lying",
      "start": 76.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 83.12000274658203,
      "text": "I just don't want you to worry",
      "start": 80.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 87.16000366210938,
      "text": "This is the part where I take all my feelings and hide them",
      "start": 83.30000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 90.41999816894531,
      "text": "Cause I don't want nobody to hurt me, can't breathe",
      "start": 87.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 92.31999969482422,
      "text": "I'm waiting for the exhale",
      "start": 90.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 95.37999725341797,
      "text": "Touch my pain with my wishes and I wish them well",
      "start": 92.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 99.0199966430664,
      "text": "Still no life, but oh well",
      "start": 95.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 101.91999816894531,
      "text": "I still try even though I know I'm gon' fail",
      "start": 99.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 105.19999694824219,
      "text": "Stress on my shoulder like an anvil",
      "start": 102.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 108.41999816894531,
      "text": "Work it got me itching like I need help",
      "start": 105.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 111.55999755859375,
      "text": "Drugs are killing me, I'm bleeding on help",
      "start": 108.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 115.72000122070312,
      "text": "Sometimes I just don't know how to fail",
      "start": 112.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 119.62000274658203,
      "text": "Hell, but let's keep it real",
      "start": 117.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 122.73999786376953,
      "text": "If it wasn't for these pills, I wouldn't be here",
      "start": 119.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 126.16000366210938,
      "text": "What if I keep taking these pills, I wouldn't be here",
      "start": 122.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 128.4199981689453,
      "text": "Yeah, must have told you all my secrets",
      "start": 126.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 132.6199951171875,
      "text": "Yeah, they're killing me to pieces",
      "start": 130
    },
    {
      "end": 135.94000244140625,
      "text": "I really think I need them",
      "start": 132.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 141.10000610351562,
      "text": "I stopped taking the drugs and then the drugs take me",
      "start": 137.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 144.5800018310547,
      "text": "This is the part where I tell you I'm fine but I'm lying",
      "start": 141.10000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 147.16000366210938,
      "text": "Cause I just don't want you to worry",
      "start": 144.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 151.27999877929688,
      "text": "This is the part where I take all my feelings and hide them",
      "start": 147.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 154.44000244140625,
      "text": "Cause I don't want nobody to hurt me, can't breathe",
      "start": 151.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 156.33999633789062,
      "text": "I'm waiting for the exhale",
      "start": 154.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 159.44000244140625,
      "text": "Touch my pain with my wishes and I wish them well",
      "start": 156.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 162.74000549316406,
      "text": "Still no life, but oh well",
      "start": 159.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 166.3800048828125,
      "text": "Still try even though I know I'm gon' fail",
      "start": 162.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 168.74000549316406,
      "text": "Stress on my shoulder like an anvil",
      "start": 166.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 172.5399932861328,
      "text": "Work it got me itching like I need help",
      "start": 169.5
    },
    {
      "end": 175.5800018310547,
      "text": "Drugs are killing me, I'm bleeding on help",
      "start": 172.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 179.89999389648438,
      "text": "Sometimes I just don't know how to fail",
      "start": 176
    },
    {
      "end": 185.74000549316406,
      "text": "Sometimes I just don't know how to feel",
      "start": 182.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 191.63999938964844,
      "text": "This is the part where I tell you I'm fine",
      "start": 188.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 213.33999633789062,
      "text": "This is the part where I take all my feelings and hide them",
      "start": 213.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 213.36000061035156,
      "text": "Cause I don't want nobody to hurt me, can't breathe",
      "start": 213.33999633789062
